# newstile Converter

This converter converts a newstile element tree into a newstile document and supports all available
element types. This converter, together with the [HTML parser](../parser/html.html), can be used to
convert HTML documents to newstile documents.

Another use would be to format a badly styled newstile document (i.e. one with wrapped lines,
multiple different indentations used in one list, ...).


